## Take Our Pre-Survey

#### To better gauge your learning and improve this professional learning course, please take our <a href="https://studio.code.org/form/selfpaced_pd_equity_cs_pilot_pre_survey" target="blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Equity in Computer Science pre-survey</a>.

